Class FlipFitGymOwnerBusiness

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.business.FlipFitGymOwnerBusiness
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFlipFitGymOwner
public class FlipFitGymOwnerBusiness extends Object implements IFlipFitGymOwner
Business logic for managing FlipFit gym owners. Implements operations for adding gym centres, slots, viewing centres, payments, editing owner details, and registration.
